dct_title_s: A new map of the county of Westmoreland
dct_description_sm: Latitudinal and longitudinal lines along margins.
Legend at bottom left; index in lower right; title in upper left.
Shows topography, waterways, routes, notable houses.
Appears in Smith's New English atlas containing distinct maps of all the principal empires... throughout the world, London, 1801.
dct_publisher_sm: printed for C. Smith No. 172 Strand
